The NFS persistent state directory is /var/lib/nfs

Server
------

Exports:
/var/lib/nfs/etab

Mounts from client (information may not be reliable):
/var/lib/nfs/rmtab

Lock and notification status:
/var/lib/nfs/statd/sm/*
/var/lib/nfs/statd/state

nfsd settings:
/proc/fs/nfsd/*


Client
------

Lock and notification status:
/var/lib/nfs/statd/sm/*
/var/lib/nfs/statd/state
